# _MainProject Code Boundaries

- Keep game feature code in `Assets/_MainProject/Scripts/...`.
- Keep runtime code and editor code separated; editor helpers belong in `Editor/`.
- Do not place new game logic in `Packages/com.ohze.gameup.core/...`; extend from `Assets/_MainProject` instead.
- Respect GameUp Core APIs first (`GULogger`, `Signal`, `UIScreen`/`UIPopup`, `GUPool`) before custom reinventions.
- Keep feature folders vertical where possible (`Feature/Runtime`, `Feature/Editor`, `Feature/Tests`) to reduce coupling.
